助教資訊 Contact with Tutor
       The work scope of the TA is explained below: 
(1) 協助課程準備工作（如翻譯、校稿、打字、影印、製作簡報、教材準備、資料收集與分析等）；
(2) 協助教師教學工作（如協助命題、改考卷、執勤解題、批改作業、學生課業輔導、課程支援、登錄核定成績、協助實習課程、查堂點名、教學網頁設計、協助電腦軟體應用教學、教學設備操作等）      

學習規範 Course Policy
	    Classrooms (教室):
First week at Room 7405, Weinong Building.
Odd weeks at Lab 26102, Hsiu-chi Building.
單數週上課教室：修齊大樓一樓 26102 教室
Even weeks at Room 7405, Weinong Building.
雙數週上課教室：唯農大樓 7405 教室

Attendance (出席率):
1. Roll calls are performed each class. Students with full attendance will earn 2 extra points for their final scores. All kinds of leaves, except the business ones, will not be accepted.
每堂課上課點名，全勤學生期末總分加兩分。除公假外，任何假由皆不受理。
2. Students who are going to be on a business trip have to excuse themselves in advance. Proof prior to the leave.
公假者請提早告知，並出示公假單。

Participation (課堂參與):
1. Students have to volunteer to speak in class in order to get points for participation. They get 1 point every time they volunteer to answer a question in English correctly, and that means they need to volunteer for at least 15 times.
學生上課必須自動發言，課堂參與才能加分。每舉手發言回答問題，答對一次，加 1 分，整學期至少需發言 15 次，方達滿分 15 分。
2. There are two types of participation points: group based (10%) and individual based (5%). Students have to earn 5 points for individual participation in order to accumulate more points for group-based volunteering. Those who have not gotten 5 individual points can only earn 10 points for group-based volunteering at max. 
課堂參與分為小組與個人得分。若個人參與分數未達 5 分者，小組參與分數最多只得 10 分，無法繼續累計。
3. Students whose points for participation have exceeded the maximum (15%) will get 15 points for this item. Those who have gotten 30 points will get 1 extra point.
若課堂參與加分已超過 15 分者，以 15 分計算。若超過 30 分者，可再追加一分。以此類推。
4. To ensure students' learning effectiveness, material readiness will be assessed in this class. Students who are found to fail to bring the right course materials to each class will face loss of 1 point (1%) for Participation.
為確保學習成效，未帶該堂課所需教材者，每次扣課堂參與項目一分（亦即總分一分）。

In-class Practice (課堂練習):
1. Students have to practise oral English at least 2 times during the semester. 
本學期學生必須練習口說至少兩次。
2. Each time they try, they can gain at least 5 semester points at maximum depending on their performance.
每次練習視上臺表現而定，一次最多可得總分五分。
3. Grading criteria will be given in class based on the learning objectives.
給分標準視每堂課學習目標而定。

Quizzes (隨堂考):
Students will be tested on the vocabulary upon the completion of each article being taught. Make sure you use test sheet for quizzes, or 0 will be granted.
每上完一課抽考單字，未使用隨堂測驗紙者 0 分計算。

Assignments (作業): 
Students are supposed to submit a copy of PPT slides by the deadline. Those who fail to hand in the assignment before the deadline are going to lose 5 semester points.
同學需在指定日期列印並繳交小組報告之 PPT，遲交或未繳交小組扣總分 5 分。

Midterm Exam – Individual Presentation (期中考—個人簡報):
1. The midterm exam, which is going to be scheduled on Weeks 13 and 14, is in the form of individual presentation. You are going to make a presentation based on the lessons taught.
期中考為個簡報，同學需在第 13 與 14 週針對上課所學內容做簡短簡報。
2. More details will be announced in class.
更多細節將於課堂中宣佈。

Presentations (小組報告):
1. Students will be divided into groups of four or five (no more than five).
每組小組 4 到 5 位同學，最多不可超過 5 位。
2. Each group has to present once. The presentation accounts for 35% of the total points. Group-based presentations are going to take place on Weeks 17 & 18. If students are absent on either week, 5% is going to be taken away.
本學期總共有一次小組報告，佔總分 35 分。報告時間為第 17 與 18 週，學生任一週缺席將損失總分 5 分。
3. All the members have to present on the stage. Your performance will be assessed as a group, so the results will be shared by all the members.所有組員皆須上臺報告，因此成績以小組為主。
4. More details will be announced in class.
更多細節將於課堂中宣佈。

Housekeeping Announcements (上課相關事項):
Check Moodle on a regular basis. Announcements and course materials will be posted on Moodle.
請定期查看 Moodle 上公佈的資訊與上傳之課程補充教材。
Download handouts and supplementary materials, if any, before class.
請於課前下載與列印講義與補充教材。
Students are responsible for missed assignments or exams due to disregard for Moodle.
若因疏於查看 Moodle 而遺漏繳交任何作業或小考，學生需自行負責。      

