課程概述 Course Description
       建立企業經營管理之知識，並加強英語溝通技能。 

課程學習目標 Course Objectives
To familiarise students with knowledge related to business management;To increase students' command of related vocabulary and terminology;To improve students' communication skills such as making presentations, etc. 

